high_descs: Turn around and go to the wall between the table and the garbage bag on the floor, then turn to the table on your right.
Pick up the loaf of bread on the back of the table.
Turn to your right and go across the room to the refrigerator.
Place the loaf of bread on the top shelf of the refrigerator, wait a moment for it to chill, then remove the loaf of bread from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go back to the white table across from you.
Place the loaf of bread nest to the spatula, on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold loaf of bread on the table.

high_descs: Turn right, then right again and face the table to your right.
Take the bread off of the table in front of you.
Turn right and face the fridge in front of you.
Place the bread in the fridge, take it out and close it.
Turn around and face the table to your right.
Place the bread on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place cold bread on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the corner then turn right and face the table.
Pick up the bread from the table.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Put the bread in the fridge to cool off for a moment then take it back out.
Turn around and walk to the corner then turn right to face the table.
Put the bread on the table behind the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put a cool loaf of bread on the table.
